title: Donaldson trades words with Kela, benches clear in ALDS
text:
> Texas Donaldson trades words with Kela, benches clear in ALDS Texas Rangers' Keone Kela, right, is held back by teammate catcher Chris Gimenez, center, during the 13th inning of baseball Game 2 of the American League Division Series against the Toronto Blue Jays in Toronto, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
